### Technical Architecture

#### Tech Stack (from [[Projects/Lazy Golfing]])

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|-------|------------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 15 (App Router) | SSR, great DX |
| **UI** | React 19, TypeScript | Modern, type-safe |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Rapid development |
| **Backend** | NestJS 11 | Enterprise patterns, scalable |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL | Relational data, Prisma ORM |
| **Auth** | NextAuth.js or Clerk | Quick setup |
| **Hosting** | Vercel (FE) + Railway (BE) | Cheap, scalable |

#### Database Schema (Simplified)

```prisma
model User {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  email     String   @unique
  name      String
  avatar    String?
  leagues   LeagueMember[]
  rounds    Round[]
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}

model League {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  name        String
  description String?
  settings    Json     // scoring rules, etc.
  inviteCode  String   @unique
  members     LeagueMember[]
  rounds      Round[]
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
}

model LeagueMember {
  id        String @id @default(uuid())
  user      User   @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  userId    String
  league    League @relation(fields: [leagueId], references: [id])
  leagueId  String
  role      Role   @default(MEMBER)
  handicap  Float?

  @@unique([userId, leagueId])
}

model Round {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  date      DateTime
  course    String
  score     Int
  user      User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  userId    String
  league    League?  @relation(fields: [leagueId], references: [id])
  leagueId  String?
  holes     Json?    // Per-hole breakdown
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}

enum Role {
  OWNER
  ADMIN
  MEMBER
}
```

