**Title:** "I Dropped My Average from 120 to 60 in ONE MONTH with This Simple Trick!"

**Hook:** Clickbait that delivers - but not what you expect

**Script Outline:**

```
[0:00-0:30] INTRO
- Dramatic music, scorecard comparison
- "One simple trick that the PGA doesn't want you to know..."

[0:30-2:00] THE REVELATION
- "The trick is... cheating"
- But wait - hear us out
- "If you're not playing for money, who cares?"

[2:00-6:00] THE LAZY GOLFER'S RULEBOOK
- Gimme putts (anything inside the leather)
- Breakfast balls (first tee mulligan, always)
- Foot wedges (kick it to a better lie)
- Gallery rules (ball always found in good spot)
- Winter rules (every day is winter)
- Strategic scoring (par 5s are actually par 6s for us)

[6:00-8:00] THE PHILOSOPHY
- Golf is supposed to be fun
- Nobody cares about your score except you
- Relaxation > competition

[8:00-9:00] CALL TO ACTION
- Subscribe for more lazy golf content
- Check out the apparel
- Join the community
```

