## Risk Assessment

### High Impact Risks

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| **Brand doesn't resonate** | Medium | High | Test early with target audience, iterate quickly |
| **Co-founder misalignment** | Low | High | Clear operating agreement, regular check-ins |
| **Quality issues (apparel)** | Medium | High | Sample thoroughly, start with POD |
| **Platform too complex** | Medium | Medium | MVP discipline, user feedback |
| **Cash flow problems** | Low | High | Start lean, revenue before scale |

### Medium Impact Risks

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| **Competition enters** | Medium | Medium | First mover advantage, authentic brand |
| **YouTube doesn't grow** | High | Low | It's marketing, not core business |
| **Trademark issues** | Low | Medium | Proper search, attorney review |
| **Supply chain delays** | Medium | Medium | POD model reduces risk |

### Market Risks

| Risk | Response |
|------|----------|
| Golf popularity declines | Diversify into general outdoor/leisure |
| Economic downturn | Golf apparel is discretionary - adjust pricing |
| Major competitor (Nike, etc.) enters space | They can't be authentic/funny like us |

